{
  "stem": "13315.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Originally, so far as I had the impression traveling in those circles, they didn't mean to kill all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wanted to get the Jews out of Europe, conquer Europe, and make it a German Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, he said that time, look, today's Germans are no Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are not racially pure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would have to found a society that gradually purifies them-- some blond, blue-eyed girls and boys, put them into what they called schools, or whatever you want to call it, where they would create new Aryan children.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Aryan concept was the craziest thing to anybody who thought about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the Aryans were some people in ancient India.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Germans never came from India.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Aryans in India meant the noble ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For-- for example, one thing-- Father, even though he was Jewish, he was probably the only Jew in the tailor organization-- customs tailors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, that was still on the old principles built-- they were still, so to say, privileged.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was the financial man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then later on, he said to have spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of them are Catholic socialists-- socials.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wanted to relinquish the job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, no, stay with-- stay with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, no, I don't belong any more to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he stopped right then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, when they came to power, they-- he had to close up shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't use any of their material.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took an inventory of the materials.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was not any more ours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- from that moment on, we felt it immediately, even though much of the population sympathized with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't dare to show it too openly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, how did the people around you treat you personally?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
